The Sailors outside of town does great pub food as does PF McCarthys.
Boxed Wood Fired Pizza on The Square is a favourite here and tonight Im going to Lily House, possibly the best Chinese in the country.

@AmyH70 Size of water surface area is best kept large as possible - like an inverted funnel. It need not be too deep in the water, an inch or 2.
Search: "inches of water" 4 pressures.
Test your prototype by feeding a home vacuum cleaner bags' contents into it. C+Hepa will catch the rest.
